name: 40hzBinauralBeatsforInsaneFocus
0:
”Alexa open forty hertz binaural beats”
”Alexa ask forty hertz binaural beats to play for 30 minutes”
”Alexa stop”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: forty hertz binaural beats
des:
These Binaural Beats are perfect for insanely DEEP focus sessions. 

All you need to do is say Alexa start Forty Hertz Binaural Beats, and she will play the track for 30 minutes. This is a perfect skill to leave on while you are asleep, to use for relaxation and meditation, or to tune in and focus on your work.
